OL,5, A claim by a committee of MPs that HM  
OL,6, Revenue and Customs (HMRC) looks "soft 
OL,7, on fraud" has been met by a robust     
OL,8, response by the tax authority.         
OL,10,FInaction over tracking down fraudulent 
OL,11,Fclaims for Covid support risked        
OL,12,F"rewarding the unscrupulous", the      
OL,13,FPublic Accounts Committee (PAC) said.  
OL,15,FBut HMRC said that it rejected many of 
OL,16,Fthe statements in the PAC report.      
OL,18,FTreasury minister Lord Agnew recently  
OL,19,Fresigned over what he called schoolboy 
OL,20,Ferrors relating to Covid grants.       
